title: #92Noon! Evason/Snob/Sandelin/Parrish/Carter
description: Wild coach Dean Evason starts the show, then Stump the Snob finishes the first hour....Final hour features UMD head coach Scott Sandelin, then Mark Parrish and Ryan Carter give love for their respective Huskies and Mavs! Vikings/NFL talkers stuffed in the middle.
